      <title>法国呼吁欧盟将巴塞尔交易规则延期一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/france-calls-for-eu-to-delay-basel-trading-rules-by-extra-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英国将新的银行资本规则实施推迟至 2027 年之后，法国当局呼吁欧盟同意比原计划更长时间暂缓实施该规则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/france-calls-for-eu-to-delay-basel-trading-rules-by-extra-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 12:02:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
