      <title>关税风险缓解令欧元本周有望创一年来最佳表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/euro-poised-for-its-best-week-in-a-year-on-easing-tariff-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在投资者降低对降息的预期并押注美国贸易关税不会像之前担心的那样尽快生效后，欧元有望创下一年多以来的最佳一周表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-24/euro-poised-for-its-best-week-in-a-year-on-easing-tariff-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 10:32:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
